N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 1 ยง 20.54 - Use of equivalent price or index

State Regulations

If for any reason a price or index specified by this Part
for use in computing class prices or other purposes is not reported or
published in the manner therein described, the market administrator shall use a
price or index determined by the Secretary to be equivalent to or comparable
with the price or index specified. Notes
